#: ../../source/KLExtensionsGuide/SceneGraph/scenegraphoverview.rst:413
msgid ""
":kl-ref:`SceneGraph.getByPropertyNameGlobalVersions`: a global observer "
"for changes related to all property with a given name."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/KLExtensionsGuide/SceneGraph/scenegraphoverview.rst:416
msgid ""
":kl-ref:`SceneGraph.addInstancesObserver`: a global observer for any "
"added object instances (or sub-instances) or hierarchy changes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/KLExtensionsGuide/SceneGraph/scenegraphoverview.rst:421
msgid ""
"The :kl-ref:`SGIncrementalObserver` object allows to efficiently cumulate"
" scene graph changes as a compact and centralized `changes history`, "
"allowing clients (such as :ref:`sceneassembly`) to update asynchronously."
" Only the required changes are kept (history scanned by all clients is "
"flushed)."
