#: ../../source/KLExtensionsGuide/SceneGraph/scenegraphoverview.rst:563
msgid ""
":kl-ref:`SGObjectProperty` (:kl-ref:`SGObjectProperty.setGenerator`): "
"when SGObjectProperty data is requested (value, type, version), the :kl-"
"ref:`SGObjectProperty.waitingGenerator` method indicates that it has not "
"finish to evaluate yet (background exection pending). The :kl-"
"ref:`SGObjectProperty.forceGenerate` method will wait for an asynchronous"
" value to be ready, at the cost of performance (no gains from computing "
"in backgound at that point)."
